description:
Aryna Sabalenka and Emma Navarro are scheduled to play each other in a semifinal matchup in the US Open Women’s Singles Tournament on September 5, 2024, at 7:00 PM ET.

This market will resolve to “Sabalenka” if Aryna Sabalenka wins her match against Emma Navarro in the semifinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

This market will resolve to “Navarro” if Emma Navarro wins her match against Aryna Sabalenka in the semifinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

If the match ends in a tie, is canceled, or delayed beyond September 12, 2024, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the US Open (ex: https://www.usopen.org/index.html) including live footage, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
